.
Then it came about after the plague, that the LORD spoke to Moses and to Eleazar the son of Aaron the priest, saying, -- numbers 26:1
.
"Take a census of all the congregation of the sons of Israel from twenty years old and upward, by their fathers' households, whoever is able to go out to war in Israel." -- numbers 26:2
.
So Moses and Eleazar the priest spoke with them in the plains of Moab by the Jordan at Jericho, saying, -- numbers 26:3
.
