.
Reuben, Israel's firstborn, the sons of Reuben: of Hanoch, the family of the Hanochites; of Pallu, the family of the Palluites; -- numbers 26:5
.
of Hezron, the family of the Hezronites; of Carmi, the family of the Carmites. -- numbers 26:6
.
These are the families of the Reubenites, and those who were numbered of them were 43,730. -- numbers 26:7
.
The son of Pallu: Eliab. -- numbers 26:8
.
